snippet.title: New game Cross And Crush: crush them all!
snippet.description:
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/cross-and-crush/id1147938575?mt=8
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.akademgp.CrossAndCrush

Meet new game Cross and Crush: crush them all!

Breaking news! Cross And Crush is out on App Store and ready to turn the world upside down

Hold your breath: the crazy squirrel apocalypse has begun! In this Minecraft-inspired world the battle-hardened fuzzy protagonist is going across continents leaving chaos and destruction in its wake - and you’re invited to join! Feeling eager to crush them all after a long week? Then prepare to enjoy the wild rush through the city maze, take out the enemies you’re inevitably to make and prove yourself worthy of the title of dark overlord in this wacky arcade. World domination is at stake: crush them all or die trying!
